========================================
CONFIGURACIÓN COMPLETA DEL LABORATORIO
VPN SITE-TO-SITE GRE OVER IPSEC (IKEv1)
========================================

Topología

PC1 ---- R1 ---- ISP ---- R2 ---- PC2

Redes LAN

192.168.63.0/24
192.168.64.0/24


========================================
CONFIGURACIÓN ROUTER R1
========================================

hostname R1

interface e0/1
 no switchport
 ip address 10.63.1.1 255.255.255.252
 no shutdown

interface e0/2
 no switchport
 ip address 192.168.63.1 255.255.255.0
 no shutdown

ip route 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 10.63.1.2

interface tunnel0
 ip address 172.16.1.1 255.255.255.252
 tunnel source e0/1
 tunnel destination 10.63.2.2

ip route 192.168.64.0 255.255.255.0 172.16.1.2

crypto isakmp policy 10
 encryption aes
 hash sha
 authentication pre-share
 group 2
 lifetime 86400

crypto isakmp key cisco address 10.63.2.2

crypto ipsec transform-set TS esp-aes esp-sha-hmac

access-list 100 permit gre host 10.63.1.1 host 10.63.2.2

crypto map CMAP 10 ipsec-isakmp
 set peer 10.63.2.2
 set transform-set TS
 match address 100

interface e0/1
 crypto map CMAP


